{"tid":1255960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚18區齊齊擺街站， 25號屯門晏晝同夜晚有放映會","createTime":"2019-06-24T17:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T03:37:46.000Z","uid":29820,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b56eb872ba464ddda021c76ab343f4e05830e5","tid":1255960,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"相信大家近日係唔同地區都見到多咗親建制嘅人出黎擺街站，我地都唔可以輸蝕嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯天元嘅手足請注意，依家暫定咗黎緊會有3日擺街站做放映會，目的係想比多啲人睇到cctvb冇播嘅野、解釋下點解件事仲未完、提醒番大家嘅訴求係乜、同埋為帶來不便向市民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n因為決定去馬落手做呢件事都幾倉卒，所以人手上同內容安排上都未必做得好好。街站時間長短同埋成效都好睇當日人手如何(暫時聽日下午同夜晚都係分別得幾位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。所以有時間嘅你想出一分力，不妨出黎一齊做下文宣，將我地心中嘅想法話比大家知。<br />\n<br />\n只要有心，遍花開花並唔係難事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4a7cVL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4a7cVL5.jpg&h=dca7081b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd286d657775845f240eb587de8ed7ab803b043f","tid":1255960,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T22:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3620dedc5eefd7db1c21ff52a5a5a5c4ac7e0642","tid":1255960,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T22:56:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8542056f3e743c4d1591aa820a13a260361c26","tid":1255960,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T22:58:56.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"259c0b4a0a8357755fb08300cfd7cb00e5fe8b8b","tid":1255960,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime